NOTICE OF PROPOSED CLASS ACTION SETTLEMENT
[redacted_name] v. [redacted_name], Inc., Case No. [redacted_info]
(Circuit Court for the 17th Judicial Circuit, [redacted_address])
YOU MAY BE ENTITLED TO A CASH PAYMENT FROM A CLASS ACTION SETTLEMENT IF YOU USED THE TUBI VIDEO STREAMING SERVICE BETWEEN JUNE 23, 2021, AND AUGUST 26, 2024
A state court authorized this notice. You are not being sued. This is not a solicitation from a lawyer.
For more information, visit
